      <div class="caja">
        <h3>2. Spelling ✍️ — the "magic e"</h3>
        <p>They all have a <b>silent 'e'</b> at the end: i-<b>ce</b>, ca-<b>ve</b>.</p>
        <p class="busca">ice · axe · cave · stone · bone · fire</p>
        <p class="peq">👉 Read them. Then your adult reads them out loud and you write them on a separate sheet. No peeking!</p>
      </div>
      <div class="caja">
        <h3>3. Read &amp; answer</h3>
        <p><em>Ötzi was a hunter. He lived in the mountains more than 5,000 years ago. One day he died on a high, cold mountain. The ice kept his body frozen for a very long time.</em></p>
        <p>a) What was Ötzi's job?</p>
        <p>b) Why did his body stay frozen for so long?</p>
        <span class="cuaderno">✏️ → answer in your notebook</span>
      </div>
